  "description": "The coordinates from the listening post lead to an unguarded Imperial supply depot. Secure the weapons before Imperial patrols return.",
  "narrativeIntro": "The coordinates from the listening post data lead to a canyon depot on the desolate world of Vandor-3. Imperial supply containers are stacked in the open, guarded only by a skeleton crew. But long-range sensors show a patrol scheduled to return within the hour. Move fast, grab what you can, and get out.",
  "narrativeSuccess": "Your team loads the last crate of thermal detonators and blaster packs into the speeder. The depot is cleaned out. These weapons will arm a dozen rebel cells. As you pull away, you spot the returning patrol's dust cloud on the horizon. Perfect timing.",
